#

Creamy Tomato Soup with Grilled Cheese

30 min
$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianComfort Food

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

QuickEasyFamily-Friendly

Description

A comforting bowl of creamy tomato soup paired with a melty grilled cheese sandwich, perfect for any day!

Ingredients

  • canned crushed tomatoes: 2 cans (14 oz each)
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • vegetable broth: 2 cups
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • bread: 4 slices
  • cheddar cheese: 4 slices
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
